    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 23,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "If there be for him an angel, a mediator, one of the thousand, to declare to man what is right for him,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 23,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "and he is merciful to him, and says, ‘Deliver him from going down into the pit; I have found a ransom; "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "and he is merciful to him, and says, ‘Deliver him from going down into the pit; I have found a ransom;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
